metadata.name: 001 - RED JUNGLE GYM
metadata.description:
Would you believe that before I captured these moments, I didn’t know that I’d end up at the top of these massive structures overlooking the Chicago Skyline, that I didn’t exactly plan a rendezvous with the boys on a red tower crane overlooking my city? Or that what began as a mission to find the next perfect moment in time, ended up as a hailing of the sunrise over Lake Michigan aside my band of brothers, signaling to the lens that it was time to seize the glory of a new day? 

~ Chicago is not just my city. Chicago is my playground (1/3) ~

001 - RED JUNGLE GYM - Taken from a new key residence that shines in Chicago skyline - 909’ - In Frame: Ugly Steffy, Mr ChiGuy, Driftershoots (Top to Bottom)

The series is 3 NFT images - each 10/10 Editions. Work by Wooglets.
